ChangeList.Description: Added the **delegatedAdminAccessAssignmentStatus** enumeration type.
Added the **delegatedAdminAccessContainerType** enumeration type.
Added the **delegatedAdminRelationshipOperationStatus** enumeration type.
Added the **delegatedAdminRelationshipOperationType** enumeration type.
Added the **delegatedAdminRelationshipRequestAction** enumeration type.
Added the **delegatedAdminRelationshipRequestStatus** enumeration type.
Added the **delegatedAdminRelationshipStatus** enumeration type.

Added the [delegatedAdminAccessContainer](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/delegatedAdminAccessContainer?view=graph-rest-beta) resource type.  Use this resource to define the details of the security group in a Microsoft partner's tenant through which delegated access to the customer tenant will be assigned.

Added the [delegatedAdminAccessDetails](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/delegatedAdminAccessDetails?view=graph-rest-beta) resource type. Represents the administrative roles that a Microsoft partner has in a customer tenant through a delegated admin relationship.

Added the [delegatedAdminRelationshipCustomerParticipant](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/delegatedAdminRelationshipCustomerParticipant?view=graph-rest-beta) resource type. Represents identification details of a customer in a delegated admin relationship.

Added the [unifiedRole](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/unifiedRole?view=graph-rest-beta) resource type. Represents the directory roles that can be assigned to a Microsoft partner through a delegated admin relationship.

Added the [delegatedAdminAccessAssignment](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/delegatedAdminAccessAssignment?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.  and related methods. Represents an assignment of administrative roles in the customer tenant to a Microsoft partner.

Added the [delegatedAdminCustomer](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/delegatedAdminCustomer?view=graph-rest-beta) resource. Represents an Azure AD tenant that is a customer of a Microsoft partner and has a delegated admin relationship with the partner.

Added the [delegatedAdminRelationship](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/delegatedAdminRelationship?view=graph-rest-beta) resource and related methods. Represents the details of the administrative privileges that a Microsoft partner has in a customer tenant.
Added the [delegatedAdminRelationshipOperation](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/delegatedAdminRelationshipOperation?view=graph-rest-beta) resource and related methods.
Added the [delegatedAdminRelationshipRequest](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/delegatedAdminRelationshipRequest?view=graph-rest-beta) resource and related methods.
Added the [delegatedAdminServiceManagementDetail](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/delegatedAdminServiceManagementDetail?view=graph-rest-beta) resource and related methods.

Added the [delegatedAdminRelationships](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/delegatedadminrelationships?view=graph-rest-beta) navigation property to the [tenantRelationship](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/tenantrelationship?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.

Added the [delegatedAdminCustomer](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/delegatedadmincustomer?view=graph-rest-beta) navigation property to the [tenantRelationship](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/tenantrelationship?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.

Added the [delegatedAdminServiceManagementDetails](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/delegatedAdminServiceManagementDetails?view=graph-rest-beta) navigation property to the [delegatedAdminCustomer](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/delegatedAdminCustomer?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.
Added the `DelegatedAdminRelationship.Read.All` delegated permission to read the details of delegated admin relationship between a Microsoft partner and a customer.
Added the `DelegatedAdminRelationship.ReadWrite.All` delegated permission to manage the delegated admin relationship between a Microsoft partner and a customer.
Removed the **delegatedAdminRelationshipOperationStatus** enumeration type.
Added the **succeeded** member to the **delegatedAdminRelationshipRequestStatus** enumeration.
Removed the `complete` member from the **delegatedAdminRelationshipRequestStatus** enumeration.

Changed the type of the **status** property of [delegatedAdminRelationshipOperation](https://learn.microsoft.com/graph/api/resources/delegatedadminrelationshipoperation?view=graph-rest-beta) from **delegatedAdminRelationshipOperationStatus** to **longRunningOperationStatus**.
Added the **longRunningOperationStatus** enumeration type.
